 g ride. Group will attempt to stay together\, but riders must be willing a
 nd able to maintain at least a 15 mph avg. If that is not possible\, pleas
 e consider joining the winter season short rides.\n\nCue and GPX: https://
 routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/lv-lititz-chocolate-ride-23r/\n\nHelmets 
 are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spar
 e tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around 
 a pen and paper waiver\, we require an LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP
  below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club 
 member. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id
 =60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's
  [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_
 id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\,\n\n[Rules of the Road](https://la
 ncbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_i
