SUMMARY:Sunday Afternoon Ride the River Trail 24F RSVP Required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\njoin your friends of the 
 Lancaster Bike Club and Rails and Trails Club for a Sunday afternoon ride 
 on the Northwest River Trail. Plenty of street parking around 40 East Fron
 t Street\, Marietta\, across from the River Trail Pub. We leave at 1pm and
  ride from Marietta to the Falmouth Boat Launch. This trail is paved\; any
  kind of bike will do. This is a casual ride. Please do not sign up if you
  will not stay with the group. No one will be left behind. 24 miles total 
 flat along the mighty Susquehanna River. After returning to our cars\, tho
 se who would like yummy food and drinks at the River trail Pub. Like alway
 s helmets are required and have a tube for your bike so someone can fix a 
 flat.\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we encourage L
 BC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride. RSVP also allo
 ws us to contact you after the ride if needed. If you do not RSVP you are 
 not covered by the club excess accident insurance policy\; only club membe
 rs who RSVP are covered.\nRichard Conner\, leader 717-572-8480
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3137132
 79/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260309T160129Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T160129Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
